      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>hake fillet[s]</strong> and cook, covered, for 6-8 min or until cooked through and coated in sauce</p><p>Stir the <strong>Thai basil leaves </strong>through the sauce – this is your <strong>red Thai-style cashew hake</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p><p>Fluff your <strong>cooked rice</strong> with a fork</p>",
