      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>fluffy rice</strong> in a bowl with the <strong>red Thai-style cashew hake </strong>and <strong>soy greens </strong>to the side (discard the lemongrass outer layers!)</p><p>Drizzle any sauce from the pan over the top of the hake</p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>caramelised cashews</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
